# Nurul Hikmah School App - Cursor Rules

## Tech Stack

- Backend: Laravel 12, PHP 8.3+, MySQL 8.0, File cache (NO REDIS), Sanctum
- Frontend: React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Radix UI (shadcn), TanStack Query v5, Zod, Tailwind v4, Workbox PWA

## Database

- Every table: id, timestamps(), softDeletes()
- string columns MUST specify max length
- Foreign keys MUST have ->index()
- Composite indexes for common query patterns

## Backend Patterns

- Repository pattern with caching (HasCache trait)
- select() + with() for all queries
- Cache::remember() on GET, clear on CUD
- API Resources for responses
- Form Requests for validation

## Frontend Patterns

- ALL forms: Zod validation in src/schemas/
- ALL API calls: TanStack Query in src/hooks/
- Radix UI components in src/components/ui/
- Bahasa Indonesia for UI text
- Mobile-first design
